import React from 'react'

const CreateToDo = () => {
  return (
    <form className='AddTodo' >
        <label>Create ToDo</label>
        <input></input>
        <select>
            Select complexity:
            <option value="Easy">Easy</option>
            <option value="Medium">Medium</option>
            <option value="Hard">Hard</option>
        </select>
        <button></button>
    </form>
  )
}

export default CreateToDo
